SELECT di.input, count(*) as valeur
FROM dart_input di
INNER JOIN player p ON di.id_player = p.id_player
INNER JOIN game g ON g.id_game = di.id_game
INNER JOIN game_type gt ON g.id_game_type = gt.id_game_type
WHERE p.username = "$player" 
AND g.active = false
AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%"
GROUP BY input
order by score;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total, p.username as Joueur
FROM game g 
LEFT JOIN player p ON g.id_player_win = p.id_player
INNER JOIN game_type gt ON g.id_game_type = gt.id_game_type

WHERE g.active = 0 AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%" GROUP BY id_player_win;

SELECT p.username,
COUNT(distinct di.id_dart_input) as result,
(SELECT COUNT(*) AS counter FROM dart_input di INNER JOIN game g ON g.id_game = di.id_game INNER JOIN game_type gt ON gt.id_game_type = g.id_game_type WHERE p.id_player = di.id_player AND input LIKE "SBULL" AND g.active = false AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%") AS DEMIBULL,
(SELECT COUNT(*) AS counter FROM dart_input di INNER JOIN game g ON g.id_game = di.id_game INNER JOIN game_type gt ON gt.id_game_type = g.id_game_type WHERE p.id_player = di.id_player AND input LIKE "DBULL" AND g.active = FALSE AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%") AS BULL,
(SELECT COUNT(*) AS counter FROM dart_input di INNER JOIN game g ON g.id_game = di.id_game INNER JOIN game_type gt ON gt.id_game_type = g.id_game_type WHERE p.id_player = di.id_player AND input LIKE "T20" AND g.active = FALSE AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%") AS T20
FROM  player p 
LEFT JOIN dart_input di 
ON di.id_player = p.id_player
INNER JOIN game g ON di.id_game = g.id_game
INNER JOIN game_type gt ON gt.id_game_type = g.id_game_type
WHERE gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%"
GROUP BY p.username;

SELECT g.game_name, AVG(score) as Moyenne FROM dart_input di 
INNER JOIN player p ON di.id_player = p.id_player 
INNER JOIN game g ON g.id_game = di.id_game
INNER JOIN game_type gt
	ON gt.id_game_type = g.id_game_type
WHERE p.username LIKE "$player"
AND g.active = false
AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%"
GROUP BY di.id_game
ORDER BY di.id_game DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT AVG(score) as value FROM dart_input di
INNER JOIN game g
	ON g.id_game = di.id_game
INNER JOIN game_type gt
	ON gt.id_game_type = g.id_game_type
INNER JOIN player p
	ON p.id_player = di.id_player
WHERE gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%"
AND p.username LIKE "$player"
AND g.active = FALSE
GROUP BY g.id_game
ORDER BY g.id_game DESC

	ON g.id_game = di.id_game

SELECT di.input, count(*) as valeur
FROM dart_input di
INNER JOIN player p ON di.id_player = p.id_player
INNER JOIN game g ON g.id_game = di.id_game
INNER JOIN game_type gt ON g.id_game_type = gt.id_game_type
WHERE p.username = "$player" 
AND g.active = false
AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%"
GROUP BY input
order by score;

SELECT @id:= @id - 1 id, dires.score as value 
FROM (
SELECT di.score, di.id_dart_input FROM dart_input di
INNER JOIN player p ON di.id_player = p.id_player
INNER JOIN game g ON  g.id_game = di.id_game
INNER JOIN game_type gt ON g.id_game_type = gt.id_game_type
WHERE p.username LIKE "$player" 
AND gt.label NOT LIKE "%TRAINING%"
AND g.active = 0
ORDER BY di.id_dart_input DESC LIMIT 100
) dires, (SELECT @id := 100) m ;
